citations:
    citation-adwd-reek-i:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "Reek I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Theon Greyjoy, called Reek. Theon has been broken and renamed 'Reek' by Ramsay Bolton (bastard son of Roose Bolton). He is held as a tormented slave at the Dreadfort, his identity erased through systematic torture and abuse. Theon/Reek is assigned to assist Ramsay with the siege and taking of Moat Cailin, using his identity as a Greyjoy to negotiate surrender from the ironborn holding it. Ramsay's cruelty and sadism are established in detail."
